        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_000860_0001" n="0001"/><!-- Change both @facs and @n -->
	
<opener>
<lb/><dateline rend="right"><add place="above marginleft" rend="gray" hand="#U">G.13.b.45(47.1)</add> <placeName><geogName type="banks">Banks of <placeName><geogName type="river"><choice><abbr>R.</abbr><expan>River</expan></choice> Chobe</geogName></placeName></geogName></placeName> 
<lb/><date when="1855-09-12">12 <choice><abbr>Sep<hi rend="sup">t</hi></abbr><expan>September</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>/55</abbr><expan>1855</expan></choice></date></dateline>
<lb/><persName>Alfred Duprat Esquire</persName>    
<lb rend="center"/><salute>My Dear Sir</salute><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
</opener>

<lb/><p rend="right">I have an
<lb/>unexpected opportunity
<lb/>of sending <bibl>notes</bibl> to
<lb/><placeName><country>Angola</country></placeName> and having
<lb/>recommended some
<lb/>friends in <placeName><settlement type="city">Loanda</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>to procure and plant
<lb/>the seeds of the berry wax
<lb/>I have to beg your
<lb/>assistance in the
<lb/>matter. <space extent="1" unit="chars"/>It is to be
<lb/>hoped a <term type="nationality">Portuguese</term> ship</p>

<cb rend="vertical"/>
<ab>
<lb/>I go down the <geogName type="river">Zambesi</geogName> next month, cannot
<lb/>possibly add more <persName>David Livingstone</persName>
</ab><!-- Closer. AW -->

	<pb facs="liv_000860_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">of war in coming round
<lb/>from <placeName><country><choice><orig>Mosambique</orig><reg>Mozambique</reg></choice></country></placeName> will
<lb/>be directed to call for
<lb/>seed and it may be
<lb/>well to have a quantity
<lb/>ready beforehand. I
<lb/>expect <persName>Mr Feeny</persName>'s account
<lb/>of the wax before the
<lb/><orgName><region>Cape</region> <choice><abbr>Agr<hi rend="sup">l</hi></abbr><expan>Agricultural</expan></choice> Society</orgName> will
<lb/>be published in the
<lb/><bibl>Boletim</bibl>.  <space extent="1" unit="chars"/>and as
<lb/>more <add place="inspace">x</add> <add place="marginleft" rend="vertical">x more than double</add> is given for<!-- DL uses the inline x to mark an addition in the margin. AW -->
<lb/>the <choice><abbr>lb</abbr><expan>pound</expan></choice> of common
<lb/>wax on the banks of
<lb/>the <placeName><geogName type="river">Quango</geogName></placeName> upwards
<lb/>of <measure>300 miles</measure> from the
<lb/>coast than suffices
<lb/>for raising a <choice><abbr>lb</abbr><expan>pound</expan></choice> of <choice><sic>of</sic><corr/></choice>

	<pb facs="liv_000860_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>berry wax. Its introduction
<lb/>on the sands around
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="city">Loanda</settlement></placeName> would be a boon
<lb/>to the county</p>
<lb/><p>As you appeared to be
<lb/><gap extent="1" unit="words"/> friend of the
<lb/>Botanic garden, May
<lb/>I suggest your getting
<lb/><term type="foodstuff">Coffee seeds</term> from <placeName><country>Angola</country></placeName>
<lb/>for redistribution.  The first
<lb/>of the <term type="foodstuff"><placeName><country>Angola</country></placeName> seeds</term> were
<lb/>a few <term type="foodstuff">Mocha berries</term> <add place="inspace">x</add>
<add place="marginleft" rend="vertical"><note>
<lb/>the <term type="occupation">missionaries</term> introduced <del type="strikethrough">introduced</del>
<lb/>many delicious <term type="foodstuff"><placeName><bloc>South America</bloc></placeName>n fruits</term>
<lb/>what would you give for miles of 
<lb/><term type="foodstuff"><choice><sic>pine apple</sic><corr>pineapple</corr></choice></term> <unclear cert="high">road edging</unclear> at the <placeName><region>Cape</region></placeName>
</note></add>
<lb/>brought by a <term type="occupation">missionary</term>
<lb/>The <term type="occupation">missionaries</term> are
<lb/>all dead but the
<lb/><term type="foodstuff">coffee</term> has spread over
<lb/>the whole country - new
<lb/>plantations of it are
<lb/>discovered daily and

	<pb facs="liv_000860_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>the <term type="foodstuff">coffee</term> is really the best I 
<lb/>ever tasted. It is of great importance to have the best
<lb/>seed when commencing it,
<lb/>cultivation as at <placeName><region>Natal</region></placeName>
<lb/>I brought a lot here
<lb/>but cannot send it.</p>
            </div>

